children.name: select p1_0.product_id,p1_0.product_name,p1_0.product_description,b1_0.brand_id,b1_0.brand_name,c1_0.category_id,c1_0.category_name,pv1_0.product_variation_image,pv1_0.product_price,s1_0.sale_type,coalesce(s1_0.sale_value,0),coalesce(avg(r1_0.review_rating),0),count(r1_0.review_id) from product p1_0 left join brand b1_0 on b1_0.brand_id=p1_0.brand_id left join category c1_0 on c1_0.category_id=p1_0.category_id left join product_variation pv1_0 on p1_0.product_id=pv1_0.product_id and pv1_0.variation_id=(select min(pv2_0.variation_id) from product_variation pv2_0 where pv2_0.product_id=p1_0.product_id) left join sale_product sp1_0 on p1_0.product_id=sp1_0.product_id left join sale s1_0 on sp1_0.sale_id=s1_0.sale_id and s1_0.sale_status='ACTIVE' left join review r1_0 on p1_0.product_id=r1_0.product_id group by p1_0.product_id,p1_0.product_name,p1_0.product_description,b1_0.brand_id,b1_0.brand_name,c1_0.category_id,c1_0.category_name,pv1_0.product_variation_image,pv1_0.product_price,s1_0.sale_type,s1_0.sale_value order by p1_0.created_at desc
